(a) where a proposed partner is an individual, the full name and address, the date and place of birth and all former given or family names of the proposed partners;   
(b) where a proposed partner is a body corporate, its full corporate or firm name and address of its registered or principal office;   
(c) the full address of the registered office of the General Partnership, which must be within the DIFC; and   
(d) every other matter that the Registrar considers appropriate.

